OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775049067
OL,3,CWho are the four astronauts leading
OL,4,Cthe historic Artemis II mission to the
OL,5,Cmoon?
OL,7,FBut who are the four astronauts
OL,8,Fheading round the moon? ITV News
OL,9,Fexplains.
OL,11,FReid Wiseman
OL,13,FArtemis II role: Commander
OL,15,FHometown: Baltimore, Maryland
OL,17,FWhat he'll be taking with him: A blank
OL,18,Fnotecard to jot down his thoughts.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
