OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775049067
OL,3,CWho are the four astronauts leading
OL,4,Cthe historic Artemis II mission to the
OL,5,Cmoon?
OL,7,FPrevious spaceflight experience:
OL,8,FWiseman rode aboard a Russian Soyuz
OL,9,Fcapsule to spend 165 days on the
OL,10,FInternational Space Station (ISS) in
OL,11,F2014.
OL,13,FWiseman is a 50-year-old decorated
OL,14,Fnaval aviator and test pilot who
OL,15,Fjoined NASA's astronaut corps in 2009
OL,16,F- most recently serving as chief of
OL,17,Fthe astronaut office.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775049067
OL,3,CWho are the four astronauts leading
OL,4,Cthe historic Artemis II mission to the
OL,5,Cmoon?
OL,7,FWiseman's late wife, Carroll Taylor
OL,8,FWiseman, was a nurse in a newborn
OL,9,Fintensive care unit who died in 2020
OL,10,Ffollowing a battle with cancer.
OL,12,FAfter his trip on the International
OL,13,FSpace Station (ISS) in 2014, he said
OL,14,Fhis two teenage daughters had "zero
OL,15,Finterest" in him launching again.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775049067
OL,3,CWho are the four astronauts leading
OL,4,Cthe historic Artemis II mission to the
OL,5,Cmoon?
OL,7,F"We talked about it and I said, 'Look,
OL,8,Fof all the people on planet Earth
OL,9,Fright now, there are four people that
OL,10,Fare in a position to go fly around the
OL,11,Fmoon," he said. "I cannot say no to
OL,12,Fthat opportunity," he said.
OL,14,FThe next day, homemade moon cupcakes
OL,15,Fawaited him, along with his daughters'
OL,16,Fsupport, he said, admitting that the
OL,17,Ftoughest part isn't leaving them
OL,18,Fbehind, but "the stress that I'm
OL,19,Fputting on them".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775049067
OL,3,CWho are the four astronauts leading
OL,4,Cthe historic Artemis II mission to the
OL,5,Cmoon?
OL,7,F"I went on a walk with my kids. I told
OL,8,Fthem, 'Here's where the will is,
OL,9,Fhere's where the trust documents are,
OL,10,Fand if anything happens to me - here's
OL,11,Fwhat's going to happen to you.
OL,13,F"I actually wish more people in
OL,14,Feveryday life talked to their families
OL,15,Fin that way because you never know
OL,16,Fwhat the next day is going to bring".
OL,18,FVictor Glover
OL,20,FArtemis II role: Pilot
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
