PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775049067
OL,3,CWho are the four astronauts leading
OL,4,Cthe historic Artemis II mission to the
OL,5,Cmoon?
OL,7,FHometown: Pomona, California
OL,9,FWhat he'll be taking with him: A Bible
OL,10,Fand an heirloom for his family members.
OL,12,FPrevious spaceflight experience:
OL,13,FPiloted the SpaceX Crew-1 mission, the
OL,14,Ffirst routine six-month mission to the
OL,15,FISS aboard the Crew Dragon spacecraft
OL,16,Fthat launched in 2020.
OL,18,FGlover, 49, is married to Dionna Odom
OL,19,FGlover. Their four daughters are in
OL,20,Ftheir late teens and early 20s.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775049067
OL,3,CWho are the four astronauts leading
OL,4,Cthe historic Artemis II mission to the
OL,5,Cmoon?
OL,7,F"I spend as much time and thought
OL,8,Fpreparing them as NASA does preparing
OL,9,Fme," he said of them.
OL,11,FGlover also said he's glad that the
OL,12,Fcrew's families will be assigned an
OL,13,FEarth-bound astronaut to stay in close
OL,14,Ftouch with during the mission.
OL,16,FLiftoff "can be this terrific and
OL,17,Fterrifying moment all at the same
OL,18,Ftime, and so I'm just really grateful
OL,19,Fto that team that helps us to get
OL,20,Fready," Glover said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
