PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775049067
OL,3,CWho are the four astronauts leading
OL,4,Cthe historic Artemis II mission to the
OL,5,Cmoon?
OL,7,FGlover often listens to Gil Scott-
OL,8,FHeron's "Whitey on the Moon" and
OL,9,FMarvin Gaye's "Make Me Wanna Holler"
OL,10,Ffrom the white-dominated Apollo era.
OL,12,F"I listen to those for perspective,"
OL,13,Fhe said. "It captures what we did
OL,14,Fwell, what we did poorly."
OL,16,FChristina Koch
OL,18,FArtemis II role: Mission specialist
OL,20,FHometown: Jacksonville, North Carolina
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
