PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775049067
OL,3,CWho are the four astronauts leading
OL,4,Cthe historic Artemis II mission to the
OL,5,Cmoon?
OL,7,FWhat she's taking with her:
OL,8,FHandwritten notes from her loved ones.
OL,9,F"It's so I can hold in my hands
OL,10,Fsomething that they held in their
OL,11,Fhands," Koch said.
OL,13,FPrevious spaceflight experience: After
OL,14,Flaunching to the ISS aboard a Russian
OL,15,FSoyuz capsule in 2019, Koch spent 328
OL,16,Fdays in low-Earth orbit - a record for
OL,17,Fthe most consecutive days in space for
OL,18,Fa woman. That year, she also
OL,19,Fparticipated in the first all-female
OL,20,Fspacewalk.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775049067
OL,3,CWho are the four astronauts leading
OL,4,Cthe historic Artemis II mission to the
OL,5,Cmoon?
OL,7,FKoch, 47, previously worked on Earth
OL,8,Fobservation satellites at NASA's
OL,9,FGoddard Space Flight Center and served
OL,10,Fstints at some of the most remote
OL,11,Flaboratories on the planet, including
OL,12,Fthe Amundsen-Scott South Pole Station
OL,13,Fand Palmer Station in Antarctica.
OL,15,F"I loved things that made me feel
OL,16,Fsmall, things that made me ponder the
OL,17,Fsize of the universe, my place in it,"
OL,18,FKoch said in a 2020 NASA video.
OL,26,@yD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775049067
OL,3,CWho are the four astronauts leading
OL,4,Cthe historic Artemis II mission to the
OL,5,Cmoon?
OL,7,FWith her previous experience, Koch
OL,8,Ffeels she has "inoculated" most of her
OL,9,Ffamily and friends against worry.
OL,11,F"So far, I haven't gotten too many
OL,12,Fnerves from folks. Maybe my dog, but
OL,13,FI've reassured her that it's only 10
OL,14,Fdays. It's not going to be as long as
OL,15,Flast time."
OL,17,FShe has however, grappled with the
OL,18,Fpracticalities of leaving her husband
OL,19,Fat home with no easy way of
OL,20,Fcommunicating.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775049067
OL,3,CWho are the four astronauts leading
OL,4,Cthe historic Artemis II mission to the
OL,5,Cmoon?
OL,7,F"I really have to make sure he knows
OL,8,Fthat it's not like the International
OL,9,FSpace Station where we can just make a
OL,10,Fphone call - so he's not going to be
OL,11,Fable to call me and ask where
OL,12,Fsomething is in the house," Koch
OL,13,Fjoked. "He's going to have to find it."
OL,15,FKoch said she has long admired the
OL,16,FApollo astronauts, who seemed to enjoy
OL,17,Freuniting at NASA events, even decades
OL,18,Fafter retiring from the corps.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775049067
OL,3,CWho are the four astronauts leading
OL,4,Cthe historic Artemis II mission to the
OL,5,Cmoon?
OL,7,F"What they went through together and
OL,8,Fhow that bonded them has been really
OL,9,Finstrumental for me in appreciating
OL,10,Fevery single day with my crew."
OL,12,FJeremy Hansen
OL,14,FArtemis II role: Mission specialist
OL,16,FHometown: London, Ontario
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775049067
OL,3,CWho are the four astronauts leading
OL,4,Cthe historic Artemis II mission to the
OL,5,Cmoon?
OL,7,FWhat he's taking with him: Four moon
OL,8,Fpendants he gave as gifts to his wife
OL,9,Fand children.JPrevious spaceflight
OL,10,Fexperience: None - Hansen is the only
OL,11,Fspace rookie on the trip
OL,13,FThe Canadian fighter pilot and
OL,14,Fphysicist is not only making his space
OL,15,Fdebut but is also his country's first
OL,16,Frepresentative to the moon.
OL,18,FMost first-time fliers stick to low-
OL,19,FEarth orbit, where the ISS lies. But
OL,20,Fon Artemis II, Hansen will travel
OL,21,Froughly 1,000 times farther.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30317
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775049067
OL,3,CWho are the four astronauts leading
OL,4,Cthe historic Artemis II mission to the
OL,5,Cmoon?
OL,7,F"Maybe I'm naive, but I don't feel a
OL,8,Flot of personal pressure," he said.
OL,10,FHansen grew up on a farm, and he said
OL,11,Fhe used to plow the living room carpet
OL,12,Fwith toy tractors and pretend his
OL,13,Ftreehouse was a rocket ship.
OL,15,FHansen is also uncommonly tall for an
OL,16,Fastronaut, at 6'2 (nearly 2 meters).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30318
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775049067
OL,3,CWho are the four astronauts leading
OL,4,Cthe historic Artemis II mission to the
OL,5,Cmoon?
OL,7,FDuring a September news conference,
OL,8,FWiseman joked that their 16.5-foot-
OL,9,Fwide (5-meter) Orion spacecraft will
OL,10,Ffeel large enough for most of their 10-
OL,11,Fday trip, "until Jeremy starts
OL,12,Fexercising, then it's going to feel
OL,13,Fsmall again."
OL,15,FHe realises only now how much effort
OL,16,Fit took to send men to the moon during
OL,17,FApollo.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30319
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775049067
OL,3,CWho are the four astronauts leading
OL,4,Cthe historic Artemis II mission to the
OL,5,Cmoon?
OL,7,F"When I walk out and I look at the
OL,8,Fmoon now, it looks and feels a little
OL,9,Fbit farther than it used to be," he
OL,10,Fsaid. "I just understand in the
OL,11,Fdetails how much harder it is than I
OL,12,Fthought it was watching videos of it."
OL,14,FDangers still loom , something he's
OL,15,Fshared with his college-aged son and
OL,16,Ftwin daughters. "The most likely
OL,17,Foutcome is that we will come back
OL,18,Fsafe. There's a chance we won't, and
OL,19,Fyou will be able to move through life
OL,20,Feven if that happens," he assured them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/21
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30320
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775049067
OL,3,CWho are the four astronauts leading
OL,4,Cthe historic Artemis II mission to the
OL,5,Cmoon?
OL,7,FHansen said the Artemis II crew is
OL,8,F"taking calculated risks."
OL,10,FHe said: "We're going to take some
OL,11,Fappropriate risks, and we're going to
OL,12,Faccomplish some extraordinary things.
OL,13,FWe're going to have some failures,
OL,14,Fsome setbacks along the way, and then
OL,15,Fwe're going to pick ourselves back up
OL,16,Fand keep going."
